{"tid":2498577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台鏗鏘集《7.21 誰主真相》奪金堯如新聞自由奬","createTime":"2021-04-21T09:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T09:22:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1defbcf9f04f54e38e7d90c3670c61114b8f2352","tid":2498577,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"金堯如新聞自由奬今日公布得獎名單，港台鏗鏘集專題報道《7.21 誰主真相》，以及《蘋果日報》的《警隊僭建系列報道》奪得金堯如新聞大奬。兩份得獎作品均有使用查冊作為調查工具。另外，港台7.21專題報道據悉早前已獲人權新聞奬紀錄片組大奬。<br />\n<br />\n有份製作《7.21 誰主真相》的港台編導蔡玉玲，因製作報道時進行車牌查冊，被控作出虛假陳述罪，案件明日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/hk-discuss/2021/04/%E9%8F%97%E9%8F%98%E9%9B%86-20210421170140_e473_small.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2021%2F04%2F%25E9%258F%2597%25E9%258F%2598%25E9%259B%2586-20210421170140_e473_small.png&h=ac20248d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《7.21 誰主真相》由港台人員蔡玉玲、鄭思思、楊月芬及陳琬蓉製作。擔任評審的港大新聞及傳媒研究中心副教授傅景華指，製作團隊在事件發生一年後、公眾對事件起因依然疑點重重的情況下，透過仔細和專業的查冊、審視原始的閉路電視資料、訪問關鍵人物作現身說法，在調查報道中提出了重要、且當權者不願回應的線索，不論是專業水平，還是按公眾利益考慮，獲獎都是實至名歸。<br />\n<br />\n至於「紙媒網媒組」大獎，則由《蘋果日報》的《警隊僭建系列報道》奪得。報道由蘋果調查組以查冊為起點，輔以實地觀察和求證，並給予當事人充分的回應權利，然後予以披露。評審之一恒大傳播學院教授李少南指，敢於揭發強權做出不恰當事宜，並以事實為根據進行深入調查報道，是評審新聞自由獎參賽作品的一項重要標準，而報道不畏強權地令不當行為曝光，可促進社會進步，故此能在46份參賽作品中獨佔鰲頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/40506/香港電台-鏗鏘集-金堯如新聞獎-40506/港台鏗鏘集《721-誰主真相》奪金堯如新聞自由奬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F40506%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%8F%B0-%E9%8F%97%E9%8F%98%E9%9B%86-%E9%87%91%E5%A0%AF%E5%A6%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%8D%8E-40506%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E9%8F%97%E9%8F%98%E9%9B%86%E3%80%8A721-%E8%AA%B0%E4%B8%BB%E7%9C%9F%E7%9B%B8%E3%80%8B%E5%A5%AA%E9%87%91%E5%A0%AF%E5%A6%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E5%A5%AC&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dBX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=e03b0259\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/40506/香港電台-鏗鏘集-金堯如新聞獎-40506/港台鏗鏘集《721-誰主真相》奪金堯如新聞自由奬</a>"},{"pid":"cdad6edb17afa7342c53d385211348e7e6da722c","tid":2498577,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rthk (已死)"},{"pid":"a3a0af58aadf3d6b5a05ecb822d11c1c112488a9","tid":2498577,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fad16082dc8f508377b4afed0dcac8e9aa4713","tid":2498577,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdad6edb17afa7342c53d385211348e7e6da722c","tid":2498577,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rthk (已死)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"追封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efe829431f7d65009a4e45a52bb54d47e88f182","tid":2498577,"uid":280593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"要去Rthk fb 恭喜李百全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}